1
00:00:00,773 --> 00:00:03,786
Do you know any famous Chinese stories, Li Ming?
李明  你知道一些有名的中国故事吗

2
00:00:04,071 --> 00:00:07,253
Yes! I know many Chinese stories. 
是的  我知道很多中国故事

3
00:00:07,644 --> 00:00:09,250
Would like to hear one?
你想听一个吗

4
00:00:09,564 --> 00:00:12,240
Yes! Yes! Tell us a story!
好  好  给我们讲个故事

5
00:00:12,835 --> 00:00:17,626
Okay! I'm going to tell the story of a farmer and a rabbit.
好的  我给你们讲一个农民和兔子的故事

6
00:00:18,488 --> 00:00:21,475
Long long ago, there was a farmer.
很久以前  有一个农民

7
00:00:21,680 --> 00:00:23,857
He worked hard all the time.
他一直非常努力地劳作

8
00:00:24,720 --> 00:00:28,853
One day, as he was working, a rabbit came out of the grass. 
有一天  在他劳作的时候  一只兔子从草丛中跑了出来

9
00:00:29,440 --> 00:00:32,453
The rabbit saw the farmer and it was scared.
兔子看见农民  非常害怕

10
00:00:32,808 --> 00:00:34,417
It started to run.
兔子开始跑开

11
00:00:34,515 --> 00:00:38,008
It ran very fast and hit its head on a tree.
它跑的飞快  头撞到一颗树上了

12
00:00:38,453 --> 00:00:40,000
The rabbit died.
兔子撞死了

13
00:00:40,853 --> 00:00:42,906
The farmer took the rabbit home.
农民把兔子带回家

14
00:00:43,208 --> 00:00:45,368
He enjoyed a wonderful dinner.
他享用了一顿美妙的晚餐

15
00:00:46,115 --> 00:00:48,693
From then on, he stopped working.
从那时起  他不再劳作了

16
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:53,395
Every day, he sat under the tree and waited for another rabbit.
每天  他就坐在树下等兔子

17
00:00:53,680 --> 00:00:57,022
He waited and waited, but no rabbits came.
他等啊等  可是没有等到兔子

18
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:59,395
And all his crops died.
他的庄稼都死了

